    <textblock>
      Prospective validation of a prognostic model based on advanced PET/CT image analysis in non
      small cell lung cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Validation on a prospective cohort of patient of a predictive model for survival based on
      image derived parameters
    </textblock>
